        <div id='about'>
          <div class='aboutDetails'>
            <h2>No one gets there alone.</h2>
            <p><bold>Mentor Me </bold> helps connect mentors and mentees from all over the world. Whether you are looking for a professional mentor, or peer mentor, 
              <bold> Mentor Me</bold> is for you. Mentorship is valuable because it allows you to network, connect with other individuals that have
              navigated your desired path, and can accelerate you to places you've only dreamed. It's 100% FREE so give it a try!
            </p>
            <Link to="/login"> <button class='homeBTN'>Get Connected</button></Link>
          </div>
        </div>
    
