              <span class='testimonialName'>-Abram Labell</span>
              <span class='testimonialTitle'>Student at University of Chicago</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='introduction'>
            <img src="/imgs/profile2.jpg" alt="mentor" />
            <div class='teamIntro'>
              <p>"After teaching for 25 years, I'm excited to connect with young educators."</p>
              <span class='testimonialName'>-Karen Adams</span>
              <span class='testimonialTitle'>Retired Teacher</span>
